children.text: The Termguard perimeter termite system pipes have not been installed/buried underground in accordance with the manufacturer’s technical installation manual.
The Termguard technical installation manual states that
‘The lines are placed approximately 50mm below the finished ground level’ .

As the building surveyor has determined that this dwelling is in a designated termite zone, the builder will need to ensure that this termite system is properly installed to prevent infestation in accordance with the manufacturer’s technical installation manual.
